snippet.title: Deathwish Enforcers Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
It's 1969 and crime is running rampant! Join the Deathwish Enforcers squad and take crime down a notch! 1-4 player single screen co-op action! Meet happy hookers, flashers and drug dealers! Invade porn shoots, satanic rituals and volcanic evil lairs! Stop the evil syndicate at all costs!

Coming soon from Limited Run Games and Monster Bath Games for PS4, PS5 and Nintendo Switch.
